summary:
Complete technical analysis of VeoForge 3.4.0 Electron application including:
- Application structure and file organization
- Bytenode protection mechanism for core logic
- HWID-based license verification via Supabase RPC
- Credit-based billing system with dynamic pricing
- Veo3 account pool management with smart rotation
- Multi-provider captcha fallback system
- All IPC endpoints and Supabase tables
- Identified vulnerabilities and bypass strategies
